    "patch_code": "// This code has been repaired. The original code is incorrect because when calling stop(), the time counter does not restart from 0. Therefore, the subsequent call of getTime() will return a larger value than it actually measured. To fix this problem, we need to modify the stop() method so that it resets the stop time to the current time, thereby setting the start time again when calling resume(). Here is the corrected code:",
